for watching the program

39:26.200 --> 39:28.619
while, I'm assuming,
scrolling Twitter on your phone.

39:28.702 --> 39:32.122
I cannot wait to see all 2,000 comments

39:32.206 --> 39:34.333
agreeing with everything we've said
here tonight.

