40:28.846 --> 40:31.598
Thelma and Louise make it all the way…

40:32.474 --> 40:35.227
to the driveway before they are arrested.

40:35.310 --> 40:36.645
It's a pretty short movie.

40:37.187 --> 40:38.814
But, you know, fun romp.

